dct_title_s: Indonesia / produced by the Cartographic Division, National Geographic Society ; John F. Shupe, chief cartographer.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by contours and soundings. Includes area inset and lists of "Geographic equivalents" and abbreviations on recto. Includes ancillary maps showing rainfall, climate, population, timber exports, and economy, color illustrations, and text on verso. "Supplement to National geographic, February 1996."
